2011-09-08T10:54:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-08/billionton-syste-may-sales-fall-63-30-table-6172-tt.html
BILLIONTON SYSTE said unconsolidated sales
in May fell 63.30% to NT$17,121,000 from NT$46,657,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2011           5/2010
Sales             17,121           46,657    
YOY%             -63.30%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            140,492          298,907    
YOY%             -53.00% 
=================================================================
 